    {
      "id": "4643a7f7-1ad4-4e86-b06d-02bba1928481",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Predictive learning analytics dashboards have been in use for a couple of years, altough not many systems have been deployed on a large scale. This work is a technology acceptance model work. Authors survey university professors on the adoption of PLA.",
