    {
      "id": "8aef4d0f-0d51-4319-88da-3f9e4ffe7c4f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Reesults show that adoption is correlated with less experience in teaching, low anxiety and more positive attitudes. It is also negatively correlated with low effort expectancy and alck of facilitating conditions. ",
